{
  "texts": [
    "It is worth noting that MCQ-M questions are much more difficult than MCQ-S questions, as the accuracy of random guess drops from 25% to 4%.",
    "All questions in UrbanPlanBench were curated from PDF or Microsoft Word documents, and meticulously transformed into a structured CSV format through careful parsing and annotation by the authors.",
    "These questions were presented to the LLMs through prompts, as demonstrated in Figure 1.",
    "In the context of the urban planner qualification exams, achieving a score of 60 out of 100 MCQs correctly answered across all subjects stands as a crucial criterion for certification.",
    "These exams pose a significant challenge even for human participants, with only 10% passing annually."
  ]
}